name: Rental-icon
tagline: Fonts for use in rental, travel and holiday websites and/or apps
body: ### Rental-icon fonts for the Rental industry The rental-icon font contains a list of icons related to the rental industry: villas, apartments, hotels, cars, etc. We are also preparing a number of rental icons from well known rental companies such as booking.com and airbnb. Please feel free to submit an issue with a new icon requests, or issues that you are experiencing with the font.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
